article.description: — Rylan Jones posted 19 points as Utah State defeated New Mexico State 85-58 in the Myrtle Beach Invitational on Friday.
article.headline: Jones scores 19 to lead Utah State past New Mexico St. 85-58
article.linkText: Jones scores 19 to lead Utah State past New Mexico St. 85-58
article.story: CONWAY, S.C. -- — Rylan Jones posted 19 points as Utah State defeated New Mexico State 85-58 in the Myrtle Beach Invitational on Friday. Jones made 5 of 6 3-pointers. Justin Bean had 17 points and seven rebounds for Utah State (3-1). Brandon Horvath added 12 points. Max Shulga had 11 points. Teddy Allen had 14 points and seven rebounds for New Mexico State (3-1). Levar Williams added 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
